<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OGITECH Restaurant | Automated Food Management System</title>
    
    <!-- Premium Unified Browser Tab Favicon Icon -->
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='%233498db'%3E%3Cpath d='M11 2v20H9v-2H7v-2H5v-2H3v-2H1v-2h22v2h-2v2h-2v2h-2v2h-2V2h-2zm2 5h4v2h-4zm0 4h4v2h-4zm-8 4h14v2H5zm0 4h14v2H5z'/%3E%3Cpolygon points='12,2 10,5 14,5' fill='%23d4af37'/%3E%3C/svg%3E">
    
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-master: #0a0a0c;
            --bg-surface: #141419;
            --crimson: #E63946;
            --text-main: #f3f4f6;
            --text-muted: #9ca3af;
            --border-glow: #2a2a35;
        }
        body { margin: 0; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; background-color: var(--bg-master); color: var(--text-main); line-height: 1.6; }
        .hero { background: var(--bg-surface); padding: 120px 20px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-glow); }
        .hero h1 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 2.8rem; margin: 0 auto 20px auto; color: #fff; max-width: 900px; line-height: 1.3; }
        .hero p { font-size: 1.1rem; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 40px auto; color: var(--text-muted); }
        .btn-primary { background-color: var(--crimson); color: white; padding: 18px 45px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; border-radius: 8px; transition: 0.3s; display: inline-block; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
        .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.3); }
        .section { padding: 80px 20px; max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
        .section h2 { color: var(--crimson); font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 50px; }
        .steps-container { display: flex; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 30px; }
        .step { flex: 1; min-width: 280px; background: var(--bg-surface); padding: 40px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border-glow); }
        .step h3 { margin: 0 0 15px 0; color: #fff; font-size: 1.3rem; }
        .step-icon { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        footer { background: #050505; color: var(--text-muted); text-align: center; padding: 50px 20px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-glow); font-size: 0.95rem; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="hero">
        <h1>OGITECH RESTAURANT AUTOMATED KITCHEN PORTAL<br><span style="color: var(--crimson); font-size: 2rem;">(Smart Order Management System)</span></h1>
        <p>An intelligent scheduling system engineered to optimize food orders, minimize prep times, and secure instant transaction fulfillment.</p>
        <a href="/order" class="btn-primary">Order your meal here</a>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Core Architectural Modules</h2>
        <div class="steps-container">
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-icon">📱</div>
                <h3>1. Order Ingestion</h3>
                <p>Customers submit automated food processing jobs tied to distinct volume criteria via the interactive terminal.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-icon">📊</div>
                <h3>2. Queue Scheduling</h3>
                <p>The processing engine automatically sorts incoming food payloads using comparative SJF and FIFO scheduling algorithms.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-icon">🛍️</div>
                <h3>3. Token Verification</h3>
                <p>Secure webhooks instantly process state transitions, routing verified tokens directly to the kitchen monitors for dispatch.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 OGITECH Restaurant System | Core Food Operations Management</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>